question:
Which of the following graphs is a sketch of $e^{-x / 2}-e^{-x}$ for $x>0$ ?

(a)
\begin{center}
\includegraphics[max width=\textwidth]{2024_03_31_352ee694f67dc559a52dg-03(3)}
